title: Nutanix Prism: Storage Pools
agents: nutanix
catalog: os/storage
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the remaining space on storage pools in a nutanix cluster.
 Limits can be configured through wato.

 This check requires the special agent configurable through "Filesystems (used space and growth)".

item:
 The name of the storage pool.

inventory:
 One service is created for each storage pool.
